# Wiom Maker-Checker — CODEOWNERS
#
# Maps each repo path to the owner whose review is REQUIRED before a change merges.
# This is the guardrail that makes "who can edit what" real.
#
# IMPORTANT
#  1. Handles below are real (@nikhilkajaria, @shivakimothi-design). Karishni's handle is
#     @karishnipuri-star — she curates /learnings/ (open, no required owner), so she is not
#     listed as a required reviewer here. Make sure every listed owner has repo access —
#     otherwise their required review can never be satisfied.
#  2. CODEOWNERS only ENFORCES anything when branch protection is ON:
#     Settings -> Branches -> protect `main` -> "Require a pull request before merging"
#     + "Require review from Code Owners" + disable direct pushes.
#     Without that, this file is only a notification list. (See GOVERNANCE.md.)
#  3. CODEOWNERS requires at least ONE listed owner to approve. To force BOTH leads on
#     the constitution, also set branch protection "Required approvals = 2" and ensure
#     both are code owners.
#
# Last matching pattern wins for a given file.

# ---- Default: both leads are notified on anything not matched below ----
*                              @nikhilkajaria @shivakimothi-design

# ---- Messaging thesis (Shiva) ----
/messaging/                    @shivakimothi-design
# Explore sandbox: open contribution, no required owner.
# (Promoting an experiment INTO the thesis edits /messaging/thesis/, which IS gated above.)
/messaging/explore/

# ---- Wrapper framework (Nikhil) ----
/wrapper/                      @nikhilkajaria

# ---- Evaluation logic = the RULES (Shiva). Agent CODE is shared engineering ----
/evaluation/                   @shivakimothi-design
/evaluation/agents/            @nikhilkajaria @shivakimothi-design

# ---- Product briefs (Nikhil) ----
/briefs/                       @nikhilkajaria

# ---- Creative library (shared: either lead can approve) ----
/creative-library/             @shivakimothi-design @nikhilkajaria

# ---- Constitution: BOTH leads must approve (needs the 2-approval branch rule above) ----
/constitution/                 @shivakimothi-design @nikhilkajaria

# ---- Learnings: open posting, no required owner ----
# Anyone may post a learning here; rule changes are gated where they land
# (thesis / wrapper / evaluation), not on this folder.
/learnings/

# ---- Performance: shared / operational ----
/performance/                  @nikhilkajaria @shivakimothi-design

# ---- The governance files themselves: both leads ----
/CODEOWNERS                    @nikhilkajaria @shivakimothi-design
/GOVERNANCE.md                 @nikhilkajaria @shivakimothi-design
